"color: red;\">況其身死已久，枯朽之骨，凶穢之餘，豈宜令入宮禁？</span><br />\n<br />\n孔子曰：「敬鬼神而遠之。」古之諸侯行弔於其國，尚令巫祝先以桃茢祓除不祥，然後進弔。今無故取朽穢之物，親臨觀之，巫祝不先，桃茢不用。群臣不言其非，御史不舉其失，臣實恥之。<span style=\"color: red;\">乞以此骨付之有司，投諸水火，永絕根本，斷天下之疑，絕後代之惑！</span>使天下之人，知大聖人之所作為，出於尋常萬萬也。豈不盛哉！豈不快哉！<span style=\"color: red;\">佛如有靈，能作禍祟，凡有殃咎，宜加臣身！上天鑒臨，臣不怨悔！</span></em>"},{"pid":"7ccc93419f7c8dea79fbb8db5ec48de6d63c266d","tid":1903734,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280e437281cd1f3f111e5915316c5596d973b8e7","tid":1903734,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c423cb53be2dc305c0485a053ea3f80f772912b2","tid":1903734,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"講真好多慈善機構都係藍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"平時就扮撚晒要幫弱勢社群<br />\n實際上就助紂為虐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲假過賈南風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"<em>后驚曰：「卿何為來！」<br />\n冏曰：「有詔收后。」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">后曰：「詔當從我出，何詔也？」<br />\n后至上閤，遙呼帝曰：「陛下有婦，使人廢之，亦行自廢。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又問冏曰：「起事者誰？」<br />\n冏曰：「梁、趙。」<br />\n后曰：「繫狗當繫頸，今反繫其尾，何得不然！」<br />\n至宮西，見謐尸，再舉聲而哭遽止。<br />\n倫乃矯詔遣尚書劉弘等持節齎金屑酒賜后死。</em>"},{"pid":"0de74fabc37232c9947c22047a3f435701b7d06b","tid":1903734,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/14/153038_4098eb295b3f8bfd89f1cc7133d9986d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2F153038_4098eb295b3f8bfd89f1cc7133d9986d.gif&h=d5a03858&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c66bcd57ad9eae1d466d5b09593da1e27af14815","tid":1903734,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de74fabc37232c9947c22047a3f435701b7d06b","tid":1903734,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/14/153038_4098eb295b3f8bfd89f1cc7133d9986d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2F153038_4098eb295b3f8bfd89f1cc7133d9986d.gif&h=d5a03858&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpfH5xe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpfH5xe.gif&h=4d0e2c12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dedb0ec201be533e0176b4f23954ef3b3f7acdd","tid":1903734,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3eb868e38fc02534709bad4caf3649b12d3e8bf","tid":1903734,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee160e08e522766ea0101d765cf2a714e297649","tid":1903734,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"孫ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"<em>夫佛本夷狄之人，言語不通，衣服殊制，口不言先王之法言，身不服先王之法服，不知君臣之義、父子之情。假如其身至今尚在，奉其國命，來朝京師；陛下容而接之，不過宣政一見，禮賓一設，賜衣一襲，衛而出之於境，不令惑眾也。<span style=\"color: red;\">況其身死已久，枯朽之骨，凶穢之餘，豈宜令入宮禁？</span><br />\n<br />\n孔子曰：「敬鬼神而遠之。」古之諸侯行弔於其國，尚令巫祝先以桃茢祓除不祥，然後進弔。今無故取朽穢之物，親臨觀之，巫祝不先，桃茢不用。群臣不言其非，御史不舉其失，臣實恥之。<span style=\"color: red;\">乞以此骨付之有司，投諸水火，永絕根本，斷天下之疑，絕後代之惑！</span>使天下之人，知大聖人之所作為，出於尋常萬萬也。豈不盛哉！豈不快哉！<span style=\"color: red;\">佛如有靈，能作禍祟，凡有殃咎，宜加臣身！上天鑒臨，臣不怨悔！</span></em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381a82967b57631155af7dcc7469250f00841136","tid":1903734,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dedb0ec201be533e0176b4f23954ef3b3f7acdd","tid":1903734,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3eb868e38fc02534709bad4caf3649b12d3e8bf","tid":1903734,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee160e08e522766ea0101d765cf2a714e297649","tid":1903734,